description:
WELCOME TO DARLING IN THE FRANXX!

We provide a safe and friendly community for the 2018 anime Darling in the FranXX. We also feature all types of anime discussions! You can meet tons of new friends and anime fans! Everyone is welcome, even those who just want a place to chill! 

--------------------------------------------------------------

We have the following: 
- Cool roles you can assign to yourself! 
- Dedicated channels for gaming and anime discussions!
- Suggestions channel for your input to the server! 
- Cool and a variety of bots
- Many types of emotes!
- Partnerships! For partnership info, join and DM a partnership manager.
